      <description>&lt;p&gt;It is straight forward to order content in Hugo by leveraging front matter
variables. The default order is &lt;code&gt;Weight -&amp;gt; Date -&amp;gt; LinkTitle -&amp;gt; FilePath&lt;/code&gt;.
It is easy to change the order based on the specific property of interest. See
&lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/templates/lists/#order-content&#34;&gt;lists of content in Hugo&lt;/a&gt;
for more information.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
